Shellye Archambeau
CEO of MetricStream


							Shellye Archambeau is CEO of MetricStream, a Palo Alto, Calif.-based company offering governance, risk, compliance and quality management solutions to enterprises in the pharmaceutical, medical device, high tech manufacturing, energy, financial services, healthcare, manufacturing, food and beverage and automotive industries.
						







